data.description: This beautiful home has an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a large living room, including energy-efficient appliances, granite countertops, wood cabinets, and stainless steel kitchen appliances, refrigerator included!  No back neighbors!   The property includes some extra value items, it has a Westinghouse Water Refining System, Solar Panels, Outdoor Garden Patio Furniture-Dinning set and umbrella, Outdoor Electric Water Fountain, and a custom Patio deck. All included !!!  The Community has really nice amenities, please take a look at the pictures.
